        <para id="id257776">Which of the following are isotopes of <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msubsup><m:mrow/><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:msubsup><m:mi> Ca </m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>?</para>
